ZH: 我们需要租赁一个大型货车来运输家具。
EN: We need to rent a large truck to transport the furniture.

ZH: 我们决定租赁一套办公空间，方便我们的员工工作。
EN: We have decided to lease an office space to facilitate our employees' work.

ZH: 我们正在考虑租赁一辆汽车去旅行。
EN: We are considering renting a car for the trip.

ZH: 这家公司提供长期租赁服务，可以租赁任何设备。
EN: This company offers long-term leasing services and you can rent any equipment.

ZH: 我们需要向租赁公司支付押金来签署合同。
EN: We need to pay a deposit to the leasing company in order to sign the contract.

ZH: 如果你不小心损坏了租赁的东西，你必须赔偿。
EN: If you accidentally damage the leased item, you must compensate for it.

ZH: 他们已经租赁了一间商店，准备开办一家咖啡馆。
EN: They have rented a shop and are preparing to open a café.

ZH: 明天我将前往租赁中心签署租赁协议。
EN: I will go to the leasing center tomorrow to sign the lease agreement.

ZH: 我们找到了一个价格合理的租赁房源，决定入住。
EN: We found a reasonably priced rental property and decided to move in.

ZH: 很多年轻人更倾向于租赁房屋而不是购买。
EN: Many young people prefer to rent houses rather than buy.

ZH: 在城市的中心地段，租赁房屋的需求非常高。
EN: The demand for rental housing is very high in the city center.

ZH: 他们租赁了一个仓库来储存产品。
EN: They leased a warehouse to store their products.

ZH: 这间租赁公寓附带家具和电器设备。
EN: This rented apartment comes with furniture and appliances.

ZH: 租赁设备费用将会包括维修和保养。
EN: The cost of leasing equipment will include maintenance and repairs.

ZH: 租赁一辆摩托车是一种便利的交通方式。
EN: Renting a motorcycle is a convenient way of transportation.

ZH: 他们租赁了一个写字楼来开展业务。
EN: They rented an office building to conduct their business.

ZH: 她决定租赁一部钢琴来练习音乐。
EN: She decided to lease a piano to practice music.

ZH: 我们正在考虑是否要租赁一辆豪华轿车度假。
EN: We are considering whether to rent a luxury car for the vacation.

ZH: 租赁公寓的租金包括水电费用吗？
EN: Does the rental apartment fee include utilities?

ZH: 我们预订了一辆租赁的巴士来组织旅行。
EN: We have booked a rented bus to organize the trip.
